# Compliance / privacy

- Never implement password vaults, Quick Logins, or credential fields.
- No analytics, telemetry, or advertising SDKs.
- Settings stay in `chrome.storage.local` only.
- Host allowlist is opt-in; default remains pattern-scoped public access.
- Favorites export may contain business keys — warn in UI/docs when relevant.
- Credit hackmods and upstream PS Utilities authors in user-facing About/README/Store copy.
